                {
                  "type": "element",
                  "tag": "h5",
                  "attrs": {},
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Humans in space – the Mars Outposts approach and its implications"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "\n                    "
                },
                {
                  "type": "element",
                  "tag": "p",
                  "attrs": {},
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "\n                    One way of exploring space would be through collaboration between humans and robots. For example, when exploring the planet Mars, robots could be used to set up "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "element",
                      "tag": "strong",
                      "attrs": {},
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "22"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "textInput",
                      "questionId": "q9",
                      "fieldName": "q9",
                      "attrs": {
                        "type": "text",
                        "id": "q22_input",
                        "name": "q9"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " and do initial research before humans arrive. In other cases, humans could stay in orbiting "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "element",
                      "tag": "strong",
                      "attrs": {},
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "23"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "textInput",
                      "questionId": "q10",
                      "fieldName": "q10",
                      "attrs": {
                        "type": "text",
                        "id": "q23_input",
                        "name": "q10"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " and give orders to robots working on the surface of the planet. This would increase the speed of "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "element",
                      "tag": "strong",
                      "attrs": {},
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "24"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "textInput",
                      "questionId": "q11",
                      "fieldName": "q11",
                      "attrs": {
                        "type": "text",
                        "id": "q24_input",
                        "name": "q11"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " with the robots.\n                    "
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "\n                    "
                },
                {
                  "type": "element",
                  "tag": "p",
                  "attrs": {},
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "\n                    In such ways, robots might be used to work in space in commercial enterprises or "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "element",
                      "tag": "strong",
                      "attrs": {},
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "25"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "textInput",
                      "questionId": "q12",
                      "fieldName": "q12",
                      "attrs": {
                        "type": "text",
                        "id": "q25_input",
                        "name": "q12"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": ". However, the final aim of humankind may be the "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "element",
                      "tag": "strong",
                      "attrs": {},
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "26"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " "
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "textInput",
                      "questionId": "q13",
                      "fieldName": "q13",
                      "attrs": {
                        "type": "text",
                        "id": "q26_input",
                        "name": "q13"
                      }
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": " of space, and this could in turn change people's attitudes towards Earth.\n                    "
                    }
                  ]
